00:05:12.519 --> 00:05:15.320
that some have given idea to

00:05:15.320 --> 00:05:16.679
or thought to in the past

00:05:16.679 --> 00:05:19.880
of reaching some place of sinless perfection.

00:05:20.880 --> 00:05:23.200
