00:05:39.119 --> 00:05:41.540
And we find that for the believer,

00:05:41.540 --> 00:05:44.720
that sin is not something that we can take joy in

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:46.540
and something that we delight in,

00:05:46.540 --> 00:05:48.380
rather something that would cause us

00:05:48.380 --> 00:05:52.000
to regret immediately after so doing.

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:54.160
As we look at this passage of scripture

00:05:54.160 --> 00:05:58.480
and we consider the impact of a believer,

00:05:58.480 --> 00:06:03.200
of the belief of a believer and how it impacts their life,

00:06:03.200 --> 00:06:04.980
